WEBVTT

00:00:00.300 --> 00:00:02.000
Late at night you are not moved?

00:00:02.100 --> 00:00:03.666
Of course I was touched.

00:00:03.733 --> 00:00:05.233
To say it's not touching is a lie.

00:00:05.700 --> 00:00:06.666
But I dare not.

00:00:06.666 --> 00:00:08.233
The water in Yen Kinh city is too deep.

00:00:08.233 --> 00:00:10.166
I'm afraid our Tham family can never be saved.

00:00:10.466 --> 00:00:11.600
How deep?

00:00:11.700 --> 00:00:12.733
Even the name is remembered.

00:00:12.733 --> 00:00:14.666
You will know later.

00:00:14.933 --> 00:00:16.966
I won't tell you for a while.

00:00:17.300 --> 00:00:18.100
Anyway

00:00:18.166 --> 00:00:21.300
You have to be careful of these two people, Vuong Chan Vinh and Ly Thanh Hai.

00:00:21.300 --> 00:00:23.266
They are all selfish people.

00:00:23.266 --> 00:00:25.033
Will achieve the goal by all means.

00:00:25.033 --> 00:00:26.033
Not friends

00:00:26.300 --> 00:00:27.933
Okay, I know Mr. Tran.

00:00:28.066 --> 00:00:30.300
So how do you plan to deal with the Trieu family?

00:00:30.300 --> 00:00:32.400
Well, if your mother wants to die...

00:00:32.433 --> 00:00:34.333
Then try to crush them from the Yen army.

00:00:34.333 --> 00:00:35.800
If not go abroad

00:00:35.966 --> 00:00:37.833
The Trieu Dynasty will attack us soon.

00:00:37.833 --> 00:00:40.166
By then I want you and Mary to take the lead.

00:00:40.166 --> 00:00:42.566
How about splitting the acquired territory 50/50?

00:00:42.566 --> 00:00:42.966
Oh my God.

00:00:42.966 --> 00:00:45.866
You are here, we, the Tham family, owe you so much gratitude.

00:00:45.866 --> 00:00:48.233
If you can get along with Mary

00:00:48.233 --> 00:00:49.633
He calls me grandpa again.

00:00:49.766 --> 00:00:51.233
How can I abuse you?

00:00:51.233 --> 00:00:53.466
11 I will not let you down

00:00:53.466 --> 00:00:54.500
I am old.

00:00:54.500 --> 00:00:57.033
The world will be yours later.

00:00:58.333 --> 00:01:00.033
The king must also enter.

00:01:00.266 --> 00:01:02.000
The master group kidnapped the young lady.